title: The Ronnie Wood Show  [Episodes 1-15]
description:
Episodes 1-15 (aired between April and July, 2010) 



"The Ronnie Wood Show" is a weekly radio show on British radio "Absolute Radio", hosted by Ronnie Wood (Rolling Stones, The Faces) who serves as DJ, playing tracks by artists he has worked with and other personal favourites, sharing with his listeners his uniquely fascinating stories, experiences and memories and using his trusted guitar to to accompany him

In May 2011 Ronnie won the Sony Radio Personality of the Year award for this show.

Each about 55 minutes long

MP3, 44khz, 128kbps
